.
.Sh CAVEATS
This utility leans strongly on macOS-provided utilities to function.
It is unlikely to be useful to users of other systems.
.
.Sh BUGS
There is no option to force OpenStep (or binary)
.Xr plist 5
output.
.Pp
GNUstep extensions like NSDate literals are understood by
.Nm ,
but are not round-trippable.
.Pp
An option to use GNUstep extensions when converting to ASCII property-lists would be helpful,
and would partially solve the previously-mentioned issue of round-tripping,
